This place can be blacklisted. Called up this morning to see if they have charges for cake cutting. Their reply is if you cut the cake yourself, there will be NO cake cutting fee. But when we arrived, they ask $150 for the sake cutting. We told them we have called and ask and your staff said their will be no cake cutting fee. Our family decided to open the cake and share it still.

result.name: Budaoweng Hotpot Cuisine 不倒翁火鍋

reviews.text: Many hotpot joints in HK but this is by far my favourite because of the best beef slices and overall good quality and taste. Might be little pricey but this place never fail. Service was fine and ambience good. If you go out for hotpot instead of making it at home, might as well go for the best.
Nice for a big group. Food was tasty and original
Very solid hotpot experience.  The 2 flavor soup pot was great!  One side for spicy eaters, the other for non spicy.  Win-win situation.  :)
Good selection of hotpot

I don’t know why many reviewers have complained of poor service, because my extended family didn’t experience any. We had a family reunion dinner with an ala carte menu. The host was a friendly affable guy. The last time we were here, I had a dim sum lunch. So it seems Budaoweng does all three well, including hot pot.

result.name: 不倒翁中日火鍋料理

reviews.text: 不倒翁位於銅鑼灣時代廣場11樓，高消費埸所，食物新鲜有水準，地方舒適优雅，若不嫌高消費可以一試！

Sehr gute Auswahl. Verschiedenen Fleisch Sorten und verschiedene Suppen als Basis.
Miso Suppe ist Super. Gemischtes gemüse als Einlage. Auch einzeln möglich. Reis oder Nudeln als Beilage möglich aber nicht nötig da Portionen gross sind.
Etwas teuer aber Qualität passt. Wenn man mal nicht aufs Geld schaut kann man auch lange sitzen. Bis zu 8 Personen am Tisch möglich.
昨晚團年朋友食飯，喜歡它易訂位及食通天有免泊優惠。牛脊肉鮮味，紋理清晰，不柴不肥，配麻辣鍋勁度十足，肥牛肉跟它相比就較失色，下次就不要點了。羊肉也是一般。另一亮點是皇牌餃子，隻隻飽滿多蝦肉料，真的好味。中高價的火鍋，食材優及服務好。五個大男人都食到好飽。
手切肥牛好食，但償錢略貴
食物質數good, 員工服務態度極差……
